tryton
======

The client of the Tryton application platform.
A three-tiers  high-level general purpose application platform
written in Python and use Postgresql as database engine.
It is the core base of an Open Source ERP.
It provides modularity, scalability and security.

This fork of tryton hosts features not acceptd by the core of trton.org
- browser widget
- different style

You need https://github.com/mediafactory/tryton_core_daemon to get the additional features flying...
This fork is still compatible with tryton.org, but you can not use the additional features!

Installing
----------

See INSTALL

Package Contents
----------------

  bin/
      Script for startup.

  doc/
      sphinx documentation in reStructuredText.
      To generate the HTML:

        python doc/build.py

  share/
      The shared files like translations and images.

  tryton/
      tryton sources.

Support
-------

If you encounter any problems with Tryton, please don't hesitate to ask
questions on the Tryton bug tracker, mailing list, wiki or IRC channel:

  http://bugs.tryton.org/
  http://groups.tryton.org/
  http://wiki.tryton.org/
  irc://irc.freenode.net/tryton

